#challenge one : Password Pandemonium

An alert pops up as we log into TBFC workstation : “Weak passwords detected on 73 TBFC accounts!” 
Here McSkidy’s password, P@ssw0rd123 has been flagged. 
Strong Password is the only way seen . 

# Objective: To create a password that passes all system checks and isn’t found in the leaked password list.

# Steps:
1. Enter password with at least 12 characters.
2. Include uppercase, lowercase, numbers and symbols.
3. Make sure it isn't in breach database.       

# FINAL FLAG 
THM{StrongStart}

